Initializer# init(sensitivityPoints:start:end:device:metadata:)

iOS 18.1+iPadOS 18.1+Mac Catalyst 18.1+macOS 15.1+visionOS 2.1+watchOS 11.1+

```
convenience init(
    sensitivityPoints: [HKAudiogramSensitivityPoint],
    start startDate: Date,
    end endDate: Date,
    device: HKDevice?,
    metadata: [String : Any]?
)
```

## [ Parameters ](/documentation/HealthKit/HKAudiogramSample/init(sensitivityPoints:start:end:device:metadata:)#parameters)

`sensitivityPoints`Sensitivity data associated with the sample, with a maximum limit of 30 points. Frequencies must be unique, and ordered ascending.

`startDate`The start date of the hearing test.

`endDate`The end date of the hearing test.

`device`The device that generated the sample data.

`metadata`Optional metadata associated with the sample.

## [Return Value](/documentation/HealthKit/HKAudiogramSample/init(sensitivityPoints:start:end:device:metadata:)#return-value)

A new instance of an audiogram sample.

## [Discussion](/documentation/HealthKit/HKAudiogramSample/init(sensitivityPoints:start:end:device:metadata:)#discussion)

Creates a new audiogram sample with the specified attributes.
